The '''Sumatran cochoa''' ('''''Cochoa beccarii''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Turdidae]]. It is [[endemic]] to Indonesia. Its natural [[habitat]] is subtropical or tropical moist [[montane forest]]s. It is threatened by [[habitat loss]].

